Sentencas: A La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3 (LSGM)-based honeycomb-type solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with a 0.5 mm thick electrolyte wall was successfully fabricated and operated.
Titulo: Self-supported LaGaO3-based honeycomb-type solid oxide fuel cell with high volumetric power density

Sentencas: This cell shows a much higher volumetric power density than a ZrO2-based cell in the temperature range from 973 to 1173 K. Detailed results of internal resistance analysis suggest that IR loss is the predominant internal resistance of the cell.
Titulo: Self-supported LaGaO3-based honeycomb-type solid oxide fuel cell with high volumetric power density

Sentencas: Furthermore, improved power density is achieved by decreasing LSGM electrolyte wall thickness.
Titulo: Self-supported LaGaO3-based honeycomb-type solid oxide fuel cell with high volumetric power density

Sentencas: The effective area power densities are about 0.50 and 0.27 W/cm(2) at 1073 and 973 K, respectively, using a 0.5 mm thick electrolyte wall.
Titulo: Self-supported LaGaO3-based honeycomb-type solid oxide fuel cell with high volumetric power density

Sentencas: A 0.5 mm thick 4-wall cell was also successfully fabricated and operated at 1073 K; the estimated volumetric power density of this cell is as high as 600 W/L when five channels are used.
Titulo: Self-supported LaGaO3-based honeycomb-type solid oxide fuel cell with high volumetric power density
